            "verse": 4,
            "text": "[it is He] Who teaches by means of the pen"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "teaches man what he does not know"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "However man acts so arrogant"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "for he considers he is self-sufficient"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "Yet to your Lord will be the Return"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "Have you seen someone who stops"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
