        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "Have you considered whether he is [looking] for guidance"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "or ordering heedfulness"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "Have you seen whether he has rejected [the message] and turned away"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "Does he not know that God sees [everything]"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "Of course not! Yet if he does not stop, We shall catch him by his forelock"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 96,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "Such a lying, sinful forelock"
        },
        {
